<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="&quot;IMAGE_11&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORI_IMG"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The image features a dark, horizontally oriented rectangular shape with significantly rounded corners, almost resembling a squircle or a pill shape. Inside this dark, uniform background, two uppercase letters, 'FS', are prominently displayed. The letters are rendered in a light grey or silver color, exhibiting a gradient effect that gives them a metallic, glossy, or embossed appearance. The 'F' is positioned to the left of the 'S', and both letters are bold and centrally aligned within the dark shape. The overall design suggests a stylized logo or an icon."</data>
  <data key="d2">C:/MMGraphRAG/MMGraphRAG/test_runs/api_working\images\image_11.jpg</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;FS LOGO&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"OBJECT"</data>
  <data key="d1">A stylized logo featuring the letters 'FS' in a bold, sans-serif font. The letters appear metallic or silver with a gradient effect, set within a dark, rounded rectangular or oval shape that has a subtle border. The overall appearance is sleek and modern, suggesting a brand or organization's emblem.</data>
